data.description: TEXAS Living ! HOUSE THAT HAS IT ALL ! Located in the highly sought after Mason Pond area, this home shows like a model home 4 bed 3 FULL bath and a back yard oasis. RV and boat parking, views for miles! Heated saltwater pool and SPA. 4th bedroom is perfect mother in law suite or 2nd master. 20ft + ceilings, floor to ceiling windows with tons of natural light ! Big primary bedroom, primary bath has dual vanities with separate jetted tub and shower, huge walk in closet. Almost half acre backyard that includes: Covered patio, lots of seating, matching brick shop or shed. The HOA includes a fully stocked fishing pond within walking distance ! New in 2019: NEW Roof, new appliances and new fence. NEW in 2021: Culligan soft water, reverse osmosis system, water heater, pool pump and pool sweep, high end security camera system and new paint throughout ! Don't sleep on the house ! - Listing agent is owner.
